<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }
    .header p {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #0F172A;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .text-block {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #475569;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .steps {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .steps h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #0F172A;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .step:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .step-number {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-right: 16px;
    }
    .step-content {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .step-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #0F172A;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    }
    .step-description {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748B;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      background-color: #FEF3C7;
      border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .highlight-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #92400E;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8C42 0%, #FF6B35 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748B;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #FF8C42;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ¯ Welcome to AI Talk Coach!</h1>
      <p>Your personalized journey to better communication starts now</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <%= @user.name %>!</p>

      <p class="text-block">
        We're thrilled to have you join our community of speakers who practice daily to master the #1 career skill: communication.
      </p>

      <p class="text-block">
        You've just completed your setup, and your <strong>24-hour free trial is now active</strong>. Here's how to make the most of it:
      </p>

      <!-- Quick Start Steps -->
      <div class="steps">
        <h2>ðŸš€ Quick Start Guide</h2>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Practice Daily (Even 30 Seconds!)</div>
            <div class="step-description">Record yourself speaking on any topic. The more you practice, the better you get.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Review Your AI Insights</div>
            <div class="step-description">Get instant feedback on pace, clarity, filler words, and more.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-title">Keep It Free Forever</div>
            <div class="step-description">Practice at least 1 minute daily and you'll never be charged. Miss a day? That's when we charge.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Highlight Box -->
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p>
          <strong>ðŸ’¡ Pro Tip:</strong> Set a daily reminder to practice. Even 30-60 seconds a day will transform your speaking skills over time. Consistency beats perfection!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <center>
        <a href="<%= @app_url %>" class="cta-button">Start Your First Practice Session</a>
      </center>

      <p class="text-block" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        We're here to support you every step of the way. If you have any questions, just reply to this email.
      </p>

      <p class="text-block">
        Here's to your speaking success!<br/>
        <strong>The AI Talk Coach Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:support@aitalkcoach.com">support@aitalkcoach.com</a></p>
      <p style="color: #94A3B8; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">
        AI Talk Coach | Practice daily, stay free forever
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
